                    <description>&lt;p&gt;the functions &lt;br/&gt;
.getFontDescriptor().getCapHeight()&lt;br/&gt;
.getFontDescriptor().getXHeight()&lt;br/&gt;
.getFontDescriptor().getAscent()&lt;br/&gt;
.getFontDescriptor().getDescent()&lt;br/&gt;
getHeight(int code)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;do not work proper especially for embedded fonts, PDType0Font .&lt;br/&gt;
Please see the attached  file PDFBoxHeightTest.pdf where the line is and should be. The fonts were downloaded from &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.schriftarten-fonts.de/fonts/11283/dejavu_sans_condensed.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://www.schriftarten-fonts.de/fonts/11283/dejavu_sans_condensed.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
